---
const talkHref = '/talks#talk-1'
const deckHref = '/talks/2026-from-interview-to-agent.html'
const videoHref = 'https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1sQJN6rE1D'
---

<aside class='talk-card not-prose' aria-label='相关分享会'>
  <div class='talk-card-main'>
    <div class='talk-card-kicker'>
      <span>Talks · 第 1 期</span>
      <span>2026.06.13</span>
    </div>
    <h2>从实习面试到 Agent 开发</h2>
    <p>这篇文章是这期分享的文字版。如果你想看原始分享记录、幻灯片或录屏，可以从这里跳过去。</p>
  </div>
  <div class='talk-card-actions'>
    <a class='talk-card-primary' href={talkHref}>看分享会记录</a>
    <a href={deckHref} target='_blank' rel='noopener'>打开幻灯片</a>
    <a href={videoHref} target='_blank' rel='noopener'>看录屏</a>
  </div>
</aside>

<style>
  .talk-card {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 2rem;
    border: 1px solid hsl(var(--border));
    border-radius: 8px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 82% 18%, hsl(var(--primary) / 0.12), transparent 34%),
      linear-gradient(135deg, hsl(var(--muted) / 0.65), hsl(var(--background)));
    padding: 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 14px 38px hsl(var(--foreground) / 0.06);
  }

  .talk-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border-top: 1px solid hsl(var(--primary) / 0.22);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .talk-card-main {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 42rem;
  }

  .talk-card-kicker {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.45rem 0.75rem;
    color: hsl(var(--primary));
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .talk-card h2 {
    margin: 0.55rem 0 0.4rem;
    color: hsl(var(--foreground));
    font-size: clamp(1.12rem, 2.4vw, 1.5rem);
    line-height: 1.28;
  }

  .talk-card p {
    margin: 0;
    color: hsl(var(--muted-foreground));
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .talk-card-actions {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.55rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .talk-card a {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    min-height: 2.25rem;
    border: 1px solid hsl(var(--border));
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 0 0.78rem;
    color: hsl(var(--foreground));
    background: hsl(var(--background) / 0.72);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition:
      border-color 160ms ease,
      background-color 160ms ease,
      color 160ms ease;
  }

  .talk-card a:hover {
    border-color: hsl(var(--primary) / 0.48);
    background: hsl(var(--muted) / 0.8);
    color: hsl(var(--primary));
  }

  .talk-card a.talk-card-primary {
    border-color: hsl(var(--primary) / 0.35);
    color: hsl(var(--primary));
    background: hsl(var(--primary) / 0.1);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .talk-card {
      padding: 0.9rem;
    }

    .talk-card-actions {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .talk-card a {
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>
